      • enhanceMetadata

        void enhanceMetadata(BxDocument document,
                     DocumentMetadata metadata,
                     Set<EnhancedField> enhancedFields)
        Extracts metadata from the document and puts it into metadata object.
        Parameters:
        document - segmented and classified document
        metadata - metadata object containing metadata already extracted by other enhancers; newly extracted metadata are added to this object
        enhancedFields - set of fields enhanced already enhanced by other enhancers; newly enhanced fields are added be added to this set
